{"tid":826442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹過後】廢物中轉站無延長開放　垃圾車排長龍拒收","createTime":"2018-09-18T08:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T17:48:51.000Z","uid":30647,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7cdea6d7d25a42ff5f777d2480591a50f035282d","tid":826442,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:51:24.000Z","msg":"「山竹」風災後，全港多區有大量垃圾要清理。前線清潔人員忙過不停，垃圾車和泥頭車司機亦加緊運送廢物傾倒。有司機向《明報》投訴，<span style=\"color: red;\">政府在此非常時期完全沒有緊急計劃，也沒延長廢物轉運站開放時間：「口說想市面盡快回復正常，卻又不讓人倒垃圾，廢物如何處理？街道如何清理？」</span><br />\n<br />\n讀者陳先生說，新界東北堆填區周一（17日）下午才恢復有限度服務，結果是深夜11點後，沙田廢物轉運站外傾廢車輛依然大排長龍：「星期日打風，很多垃圾沒回收。環保署明知第二日會收雙倍量，加上這麼多塌樹，竟然沒有延長池口開放時間。以我所知，西九龍廢物轉運站情況亦差不多。」更令他不滿的是，環保署一整天都沒有人交代風災善後安排，廢物轉運站亦如平時一樣，在晚上11點半關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180918/s00001/33f6f94e938e18b8986eb01a46c3f060.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F33f6f94e938e18b8986eb01a46c3f060.jpg&h=7e4c152c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00001/1537254533493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F1537254533493&d=g7k2Ncn0pY6isMlTzy50xY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6e915b60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F1537254533493&h=6e924fae\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00001/1537254533493</a>"},{"pid":"7d0543ba0549e0e40d95be453c793c9b223779e7","tid":826442,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:52:43.000Z","msg":"就咁放堆填區門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c9170cc270